Package model

Class Client

java.lang.Object
model.Client
public class Client extends Object
This is the Client class for creating objects representing Clients that exist in the database. Each Client has an ClientID, First Name, Last Name, Address, Zip Code, Phone Number, Email, SalespersonID, StateID and RegionID
